Features planned for next release:

[] Re-organize filesystem when metadata changes
[] Tagging/Untagging files + managing tags using file-system operations
	e.g. mv file1 tag1/ tags file1 with tag1
	     mv tag1 tag2 renames tag1 to tag2 
	     rmdir tag1 removes tag tag1 from all tagged files
[] Smart Folders for Saved Tag queries 
	e.g. tag1 and not tag2 or tag3
